defaultWe estimate that the majority of our customers who are not deemed as vulnerable will be paid their benefits directly under the new Universal Credit arrangements, which will include the housing element which is for their rent. 
default&#xa0;
defaultThe concerns around housing costs being included in Universal Credit payments 
defaultare well documented. Tenants who are subject to sanction will lose all their bene
defaultfits and risk losing their home whereas those being sanctioned currently 
defaultdo not lose Housing Benefit.
